Let's work hard together today as well.

17
00:01:14,582 --> 00:01:16,160
Okay.

18
00:01:19,382 --> 00:01:22,282
I'm so happy.

19
00:01:22,282 --> 00:01:25,382
I feel like I can handle

20
00:01:25,382 --> 00:01:28,549
the most troublesome work.

21
00:01:30,515 --> 00:01:33,582
It was all my illusion.

22
00:01:33,582 --> 00:01:39,500
Can I really finish this by the end of the month?

23
00:01:41,215 --> 00:01:42,780
No.

24
00:01:44,082 --> 00:01:47,982
Today's tasks must be completed today.

25
00:01:47,982 --> 00:01:49,292
Because…

26
