I can't finish it at all.

41
00:02:40,082 --> 00:02:43,849
I can't finish it since all needs to start from scratch.

42
00:02:45,749 --> 00:02:48,244
Sato, you're still here.

43
00:02:48,244 --> 00:02:50,849
Mizoguchi-san, your business trip must have been hard.

44
00:02:50,849 --> 00:02:53,449
I'm exhausted.

45
00:02:53,449 --> 00:02:56,849
I must tell Mizoguchi-san about Shioya-san.

46
00:02:56,849 --> 00:03:00,149
By the way, how's the preparation of the Morga Games Proposal?

47
00:03:01,349 --> 00:03:03,582
I'm working on it now.

48
00:03:03,582 --> 00:03:05,816
We've dealt with those materials several times before.

49
00:03:05,816 --> 00:03:08,149
Why does it still take so much time?

50
00:03:08,149 --> 00:03:09,916
I'm sorry.

51
00:03:10,716 --> 00:03:12,382
Speaking of which,

52
00:03:12,382 --> 00:03:15,444
she mentioned that the handover didn't go smoothly.

53
00:03:21,149 --> 00:03:23,820
- Let me see.
- Pardon?

54
00:03:23,820 --> 00:03:25,682
You have the Handover Manual, right?

55
00:03:25,682 --> 00:03:27,052
Yes.

56
00:03:27,052 --> 00:03:30,382
Here is the document, and the file is here.

57
00:03:30,382 --> 00:03:32,082
Let me check.

58
00:03:32,082 --> 00:03:33,860
All right.

59
00:03:43,084 --> 00:03:44,182
Well, Mizoguchi-san.

60
00:03:44,182 --> 00:03:47,316
Be quiet for now.

61
00:03:47,316 --> 00:03:49,416
I'm sorry.

62
00:03:52,116 --> 00:03:54,682
That hurts!

63
00:03:55,249 --> 00:03:57,182
What are you doing?

64
00:03:58,849 --> 00:04:00,382
Sorry, I startled you.

65
00:04:00,382 --> 00:04:02,716
You should apologize to me.

66
00:04:03,316 --> 00:04:05,544
Shioya-san, I'm so sorry.

67
00:04:05,544 --> 00:04:09,316
I haven't finished my work.

68
00:04:09,316 --> 00:04:11,852
Do you two have a date?

69
00:04:11,852 --> 00:04:15,782
Why don't you take Sato to dinner?

70
00:04:15,782 --> 00:04:17,240
What?

71
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,716
Haven't you worked overtime a lot lately?

72
00:04:18,716 --> 00:04:20,249
All right, now go.

73
00:04:20,249 --> 00:04:22,224
It's your Senpai's order.

74
00:04:26,649 --> 00:04:28,416
Got it.

75
00:04:28,982 --> 00:04:31,549
Sato-san, let's go.

76
00:04:33,649 --> 00:04:37,082
Is this really okay?

77
00:04:38,016 --> 00:04:39,849
You kept working overtime,

78
00:04:39,849 --> 00:04:42,649
and I think Mizoguchi noticed.

79
00:04:43,349 --> 00:04:47,916
But now Mizoguchi-san is working overtime,

80
00:04:48,616 --> 00:04:50,949
even though it was my job.

81
00:04:50,949 --> 00:04:53,416
I feel very sorry for him.

82
00:04:56,116 --> 00:04:58,216
I asked him for help.

83
00:05:00,549 --> 00:05:02,108
What?

84
00:05:03,449 --> 00:05:07,856
I told him I hoped he could look after you more.

85
00:05:09,515 --> 00:05:12,249
Did you ask him?

86
00:05:15,820 --> 00:05:21,516
So that's why Mizoguchi-san has been nicer lately.

87
00:05:23,815 --> 00:05:28,049
Sorry, I should have asked you.

88
00:05:29,715 --> 00:05:33,082
I'm very grateful to you.

89
00:05:34,415 --> 00:05:39,736
To be honest, work is really tiring.

90
00:05:43,982 --> 00:05:46,440
If there's anything I can help with,

91
00:05:47,349 --> 00:05:49,449
please feel free to ask.

92
00:05:53,315 --> 00:05:55,568
The person I've always liked

93
00:06:00,815 --> 00:06:05,082
and could watch only from afar

94
00:06:07,749 --> 00:06:11,082
is now so close to me.

95
00:06:16,556 --> 00:06:18,772
Thank you so much.

96
00:06:23,515 --> 00:06:25,615
You're welcome.

97
00:06:27,582 --> 00:06:31,056
Let's go eat scrumptious food.

